page.content: Pond Raid.A Â£70 electric pump was stolen from a fish pond in a back garden of a house in Crabtree Lane Lancing.Gym Girls Cash Leap.Young leap froggers raised nearly Â£200 for youngsters from Lancing Gym Club.Anger As BMX Plan Fades Away.A proposed BMX circiut at Lancing Manor Park has been shelved by Adur Council Recreation Committee because of the dwindling interest in the bike craze among youngsters.Garage Death.An inquest to be held into the death of a 91 year old Lancing man.The body was discovered in an A registration Volvo at his Willow Close home.A hosepipe led from the exhaust pipe to the back window. Compiled by Caroline Dollemore,Fiona Tyler and Alison Gorham from IRENE AVENUE COUNTY MIDDLE SCHOOL LANCING WEST SUSSEX.
